## 🛠️ The Four Research Agents

| Agent | Data Source | What it fetches |
|---|---|---|
| Amenities Agent | OpenStreetMap / Nominatim | Hospital, school, railway/bus station, park, restaurant, supermarket, and coworking-space counts |
| Weather Agent | Open-Meteo | Current temperature/humidity/wind + 5-day forecast |
| Web Research Agent | Tavily API | Cost of living, job market, rental prices, traffic/commute, safety & lifestyle |
| Book Recommendation Agent | Open Library | Books related to the city's history, culture, and travel |

All four run **concurrently** (via a thread pool) for **both cities at
once** — 8 total requests in parallel, not sequential.

